{
  "texts": [
    "The forgetting of UNLEARN can easily be converted to add knowledge to the LLM.",
    "This new method LEARN matches the fine-tuning accuracy of the LoRA method (Hu et al., 2021) without affecting related tasks, demonstrating its dual nature across both knowledge unlearning and finetuning scenarios.",
    "The contributions of this work are as follows:",
    "• An efficient method to identify the subspace of specific knowledge within an LLM.",
    "• A novel approach called subspace discrimination and task removal to selectively target and remove specific knowledge without adversely affecting other knowledge in the LLM."
  ]
}